casebody.data:
In the MATTER OF the Accounting by Donald K. CZEIZINGER, as Administrator of the Estate of Frederick D. Czeizinger, Deceased, Respondent. Tina Chambliss-Partee, Appellant;
v.
Robert F. Baldwin, Jr., Guardian Ad Litem of Frederick Donald Czeizinger, Deceased, Respondent. Court of Appeals of New York. February 15, 2018

Appeal dismissed without costs, by the Court of Appeals, sua sponte, upon the ground that no substantial constitutional question is directly involved.
